# Account Setup

Better Meeting Rooms is currently distributed via **TestFlight**, and new users must follow a two-step onboarding process.

---

## 🔑 Step 1: Receive a TestFlight Invite

1. Your email must be submitted by your admin or by the BMR team.
2. You will receive an invitation from Apple TestFlight to install the app.
3. Open the invitation on your **iPhone or iPad** and follow the link to install.

---

## 🌐 Step 2: Sign Up via Web

Before using the app, you **must sign up at**:

➡️ [https://app.bettermeetingrooms.com](https://app.bettermeetingrooms.com)

1. Click **“Sign up”**
2. Enter your **company email address**
3. Choose a strong password (minimum 8 characters)
4. Complete your full name and select your role

:::caution
**Important:** You must use your company email address (e.g., `name@yourcompany.com`) to ensure that you are added to the correct organization.  
Private email addresses (e.g., Gmail, Outlook, iCloud) are not supported during onboarding.
:::

---

## ✅ After Signing Up

You can now open the app and log in using the **same credentials**.

> 📌 Make sure your company has already been set up in BMR. If not, contact your project lead or onboarding contact.
